 * SIM800 basic module with just TX,RX and RST
 *
 * GPIO0   RST
 * GPIO2   TX
 * GPIO19   RX
 * GND      GND
 *
 * The PPP ESP32 example was taken from
 * https://github.com/espressif/arduino-esp32/blob/master/libraries/PPP/examples/PPP_Basic/PPP_Basic.ino
